default&#xa0;
defaultSummary default&#xa0;defaultThe recommendations made for both Forces in previous HMIC inspections receive ongoing attention. Both Forces have been visited in recent weeks to commence Stage 1 of the HMIC inspection around crime data integrity. Stages 2 and 3 will follow in Spring 2014.
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
defaultThe detail provided within this report confirms that both Forces have, and continue, to develop structures and processes to ensure ethical crime recording in line with HOCRs. This provides the appropriate assurance that the recorded crime figures for both Forces are correct. 
